{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ea4c5fab36","title":"接见中南局第九次全体会议代表时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1cba71c36b","index":0,"year":1965,"month":4,"day":21,"articleId":"ea4c5fab36"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"588180735b","type":"title","text":"接见中南局第九次全体会议代表时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"ea4c5fab36"},{"id":"625c719eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"搞“四清”，要把民兵搞好。首先要落实组织。有没有队长、班长？组织起来没有？首先是有没有，然后讲政治，不要地、富、反、环之类，要贫下中农，中农子弟进步的可以要。地富子弟进步的也可以，真打起来他们会分化的，一部分组织维持会，插白旗，杀共产党。一部分跟我们走。地主、富农、资本家也会分化，不会全跟故人。就是要争取多数，孤立少数，各个击破。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"ea4c5fab36"},{"id":"a968b5365d","type":"paragraph","text":"民兵，第一是组织，第二是政治，第三是军事","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"ea4c5fab36"}],"page":{"id":"7cea5ad6d1","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"ea4c5fab36","start":30,"end":30}}}},"__N_SSG":true}